  "Course_Name__c" : "Course Developer 1",
  "Course_Overview__c" : "This course introduces the core programming concepts, relevant files, and scripting language for Salesforce B2C Commerce. The course teaches developers how to customize the SiteGenesis reference application and modify a Commerce Cloud storefront.",
